                    <head>GDR-FRG-Israel. Following our Telegram No. 73 of 12.4.</head>
                    <msContents>
                        <summary>Review of the situation in the GDR following the elections. The new parliament has passed a resolution recognizing Germany's crimes against the Jews and instructing the government to work for establishment of relations with Israel. Open official negotiations with the GDR are proposed.</summary>
                    </msContents>
